S.FORM: = Kahaehaeoan = Gaga mniq Sincuseyn Ufungsyang ka alang Kahaehaeoan. 27 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 60 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 90% niqan 54 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 10% niqan 6 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Saysiyat 73%, Tayal 15%, Amis 2%.
